    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"119741\">François G. Dorais</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/270676-lean4/topic/Improving.20this.20syntax/near/276325834\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It looks simpler but I don't think your idea works Jannis; how do I get case-by-case identifiers that way?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I meant exactly what Mario did, only with more fuzziness. ;)</p>",
